      "options": {
        "content": "**DNS droppage** — Queries that did not return **NOERROR** (e.g. NXDOMAIN, SERVFAIL, REFUSED). Data from Cloudflare DNS Analytics via GraphQL.\n\n**If you see \"Datasource was not found\":** In the variable **Infinity (Cloudflare)** above, select an Infinity datasource. If none exists: **Connections → Data sources → Add data source → Infinity**. Add allowed host `https://api.cloudflare.com/client/v4/graphql`, Auth = Bearer token (Cloudflare API token with Zone → Analytics Read). Then come back and select it in the variable.\n\n**Then:** Set **zone_id** to your Zone ID (Cloudflare Dashboard → your zone → Overview, right sidebar).",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
